"title": "8449: imitating",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8449",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Following the example or copying the actions of another person. Christians are called upon to become Christlike. Becoming like Jesus Christ is, however, the result, not the condition, of conversion.</p>\n<h2>The people of God are to imitate God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:7\">LEV 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:26\">LEV 20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:8\">LEV 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">EPH 5:1</a></p>\n<h2>The people of God are to imitate Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the example for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:14\">ROM 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1PE 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>God works in believers making them like Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10-2Cor4:12\">2CO 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:10\">COL 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Good examples to imitate</h2>\n<h3>Paul's example</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:16\">1CO 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:17\">PHP 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">PHP 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:7-2Thess3:9\">2TH 3:7–3:9</a></p>\n<h3>Christians are to imitate the good example of other believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:2\">2CO 9:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">1TH 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">HEB 6:12</a></p>\n<h3>Christian leaders are to set examples which can be imitated</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:12\">1TI 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:7-Titus2:8\">TIT 2:7–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7\">HEB 13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:3\">1PE 5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to imitate the good example of those who have gone before</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:10-Jas5:11\">JAS 5:10–5:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's people are not to imitate bad examples</h2>\n<h3>Israel must not imitate other nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:23\">LEV 20:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:9\">DEU 18:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:15\">2KI 17:15</a></p>\n<h3>God's people must not imitate the ungodly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:2\">EXO 23:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1\">PSA 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10-Prov1:15\">PRO 1:10–1:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:2-Matt23:3\">MAT 23:2–23:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17\">2PE 3:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:11-1John3:12\">1JN 3:11–3:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14\">REV 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>No-one can obtain salvation by imitating Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:18\">JHN 3:16–3:18</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ teaches that salvation (eternal life) is a consequence of faith in him. He never links salvation with imitating him or any other act or acts.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8-2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:8–1:9</a></p>",
